{"about_the_game":"Gloomscape is a crafting, survival, exploration FPS where you're sent to explore the foggy, unknown world, and unlock its many secrets.<br><br>The world of Gloomscape offers an eerie immersive sim where small choices can change the ecosystem around you. The level of Gloom can be lowered or raised through direct intervention, or through the ecosystems interacting with each other<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will be able to <strong>grow and harvest crops</strong>, which you can use to feed wildlife or use them to craft items.<br></li><li><strong>Fight creatures</strong> that will drop items you can use for crafting new equipment.<br></li><li><strong>Help</strong> others who are trapped in Gloomscape, or <strong>bring about their demise</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Explore</strong> strange locations, <strong>record</strong> audio logs, and <strong>unlock</strong> the mysteries that Gloomscape has to offer.<br></li><li><strong>Watch</strong> as the changing Gloom levels trigger new behaviors in the wildlife, enemies, and even the environment.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1715611795","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116040/page.bg.jpg?t=1715611795","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116040/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1715611795","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116040/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1715611795","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Gloomscape is a crafting, survival, exploration FPS where you're sent to explore the foggy, unknown world, and unlock its many secrets.<br><br>The world of Gloomscape offers an eerie immersive sim where small choices can change th